commitResults.messageTitle: This adds level 0 of the ip I have not added any parse or commands interface yet, just the greeting and exit.
I have added a next command method to handle the next input that will be added. I have added the echo function for every thing that is not a command
Added ability to store whatever text entered by the user and put it as a task
I have added the ability to mark tasks as done and unmark them as well
I have added the 3 types of tasks that inherit from tasks, Todo, Deadline, Event

I tried to add the automated text UI testing, but something is wrong with it and I don't have much time now to figure it out. I removed the previous nextCommand method as it was parsing and issuing the next command at the same time. I added a Parse class to help me get the arguments I need. The new nextCommand method checks the argument that it was given by the Parse and catches and prints exceptions accordingly.
Implemented an array list to take care of the list of task
Added a delete method and made the necessary parse command for it
I added the enums for the commands available
I have no idea what is wrong with the UI testing
